layout.house_prompt: A steampunk styled home office. The room features a steampunk desk with brass fittings and exposed gears, a steampunk style desk lamp with copper pipes and vintage bulb, a steampunk themed wall clock with visible clockwork mechanisms, and a steampunk styled office chair with leather and metal accents.
